%F A192060 a(n) = 2*(sum(k=0..n, ((-1)^(k)*sum(j=1..2*k, ((sum(i=0..(j-1)/2, (j-2*i)^(2*n)*binomial(j,i)))*binomial(2*k,j)*(-1)^(n-j))/2^j))/(2*k)!)), n>0, a(0)=1.
%F A192060 a(0) = 1; a(n) = (-1)^n * Sum_{i=1..floor(n/2)} (-1)^i/(2^(2*i-1)*(2*i)!) * Sum_{j=1..2*i} (-1)^j * j^(2*n) * binomial(4*i,2*i-j). - _Seiichi Manyama_, Jun 21 2026
%o A192060 (Maxima)
